 an Indian elephant by enveloping the prey in two seconds."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Almost invisible, this gaseous POK\u00e9MON cloaks the target and puts it to sleep without notice."},{"version":"diamond","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s body is 95% made up of gases, which are blown away by strong gusts of wind."},{"version":"pearl","text":"A Pok\u00e9mon born from poison gases. It defeats even the largest foes by enveloping them in gas."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"With its gas-like body, it can sneak into any place it desires. However, it can be blown away by wind."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its body is made of gas. Despite lacking substance, it can envelop an opponent of any size and cause suffocation."},{"version":"black","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"white","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"x","text":"Its body is made of gas. Despite lacking substance, it can envelop an opponent of any size and cause suffocation."},{"version":"y","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Gastly is largely composed of gaseous matter. When exposed to a strong wind, the gaseous body quickly dwindles away. Groups of this Pok\u00e9mon cluster under the eaves of houses to escape the ravages of wind."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Gastly is largely composed of gaseous matter. When exposed to a strong wind, the gaseous body quickly dwindles away. Groups of this Pok\u00e9mon cluster under the eaves of houses to escape the ravages of wind."},{"version":"sun","text":"Should a strange light be seen flickering in an abandoned building, Gastly is lurking there."},{"version":"moon","text":"Although Gastly is barely visible, when it\u2019s near, a faint sweet smell lingers."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It\u2019s said that gas emanating from a graveyard was possessed by the grievances of the deceased and thus became a Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Poisonous gas comprises 95% of its body. It\u2019s said that the remaining 5% is made up of the souls of those who died from the gas."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Said to appear in decrepit, deserted buildings. It has no real shape, as it appears to be made of a gas."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Said to appear in decrepit, deserted buildings. It has no real shape, as it appears to be made of a gas."},{"version":"sword","text":"Born from gases, anyone would faint if engulfed by its gaseous body, which contains poison."},{"version":"shield","text":"With its gas-like body, it can sneak into any place it desires. However, it can be blown away by wind."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Gaseous and completely impalpable. Also highly dangerous\u2014 inhaling part of its poisonous body will cause one to faint instantly."}],"evo":{"name":"gastly","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"haunter","level":1,"min_level":25,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"gengar","level":2,"min_